# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:401
msgid "Submission of the national report, validation and review process"
msgstr "国家报告的提交、审定和审查过程"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:403
msgid ""
"Building on the experiences and lessons learned from the use of PRAIS in the"
" 2022 reporting process, a next generation of the on-line platform was "
"developed for the 2026 reporting process to improve data entry, review, "
"communication and quality assurance functionalities. The design and upgrade "
"of the platform was carried out bearing in mind the following objectives:"
msgstr ""
"根据在 2022 年报告过程中使用 PRAIS 系统的经验教训，为 2026 年报告过程开发了下 "
"一代在线平台，以改进数据输入、审查、交流和质量保证功能。平台的设计和升级考虑到了以下目标："

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:405
msgid ""
"A) Quality Assurance - To ensure that national reports are comprehensive, "
"internally consistent, aligned with UNCCD guidelines and well-integrated, "
"the platform should implement robust validation rules. These rules serve as "
"quality control mechanisms to verify the accuracy, completeness, and "
"coherence of submitted data before it is used by the secretariat in "
"aggregate reports and derivative information products."
msgstr ""
"A) 质量保证--为确保国家报告全面、内部一致、符合《防治荒漠化公约》指 "
"导方针并具有良好的整合性，该平台应实施强有力的验证规则。这些规则可作为质量控制机制，在秘书处将提交的数据用于汇总报告和衍生信息产品之前，对其准确性、完整性和一致性进行核实。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:407
msgid ""
"B) Transparency – the platform should enable access to all the documentation"
" necessary for understanding how the indicators should be reported, "
"including explanations of key terms, the default data sources, definitions "
"and the methodologies used."
msgstr "B) 透明度--平台应提供所有必要的文件，包括关键术语解释、默认数据来源、 定义和使用的方法，以便了解应如何报告指标。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:409
msgid ""
"C) Ease of use – the platform should have an intuitive interface with an "
"overview country management dashboard, forms which allow easy data entry, "
"switching between national and default data sources, and upload of other "
"datasets and/or documentation."
msgstr ""
"C)C) 易用性--平台应具有直观的界面，包括国家管理仪表板概览、便于输入数 据的表格、国家数据源和默认数据源之间的切换，以及其他数据集和/或文 "
"献的上传。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:411
msgid ""
"D) Improved communication – the platform should have a transparent review "
"and revision functionality, which allows tracking of changes in the reported"
" figures and facilitates understanding of the review process flow."
msgstr "D) 改进交流--平台应具有透明的审查和修订功能，可跟踪所报告数字的变化， 并促进对审查流程的了解。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:413
msgid ""
"E) Flexibility – the platform should clearly outline the differentiated "
"reporting obligations of Affected Country Parties and Developed Country "
"Parties, while allowing countries the flexibility to adjust the indicators "
"they report—for example, by choosing to report on optional indicators or on "
"indicators generally considered not applicable to their country category."
msgstr ""
"E) 灵活性--平台应明确概述受影响国家缔约方和发达国家缔约方的不同报告义 务，同时允许各国灵活调整其报告的指标--例如，选择报告非强制性指标或 "
"一般认为不适用于其国家类别的指标。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:415
msgid ""
"Once a reporting form has been completed and all the tables in that form "
"have been filled in, the Reporting Officer can make the form  available to "
"the secretariat for review. This will lock the form so that no further "
"editing can take place and allow the review process to begin. The review is "
"carried out by the UNCCD secretariat, and is necessary to ensure that "
"reported figures are consistent and that the  reporting methodology is "
"applied correctly. To make a form available for review, its status in the "
"platform must be set to “In Review”. If during the review process the need "
"for clarifications or amendments arises, the reviewers can insert feedback "
"via comments and send back the form to the national reporting officer. The "
"national reporting officer is notified when the review process is completed "
"and if comments need to be addressed. The form will then be again set to "
"“Open” mode and the reporting officer can address the comments and modify "
"the report accordingly and resubmit it for another review cycle. When no "
"further clarifications or amendments are required, the form is considered "
"finalized and ready for the final submission to the secretariat."
msgstr ""
"一旦报告表格填写完毕，表格中的所有表格都已填好，报告干事可将表格提供给秘书处审查。这将锁定表格，使其无法进一步编辑，并允许开始审查过程。审查由 "
"UNCCD 秘书处进行，对于确保报告数字的一致性和报告方法的正确应用十分必要。要将表格提供给审查，必须将其在平台中的状态设置为 "
"\"审查中\"。如果在审查过程中需要澄清或修改，审查员可通过评论插入反馈意见，并将表格发回给国家报告干事。审查过程结束后，国家报告干事将收到通知，说明是否需要处理评论意见。然后，表格将再次设置为"
" \"开放 "
"\"模式，报告官员可以处理评论意见，对报告进行相应的修改，并重新提交给另一个审查周期。如果不需要进一步澄清或修改，表格即被视为定稿，可最后提交给秘书处。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:423
msgid ""
"Building on the lessons learned from the 2022 reporting process, a number of"
" system validation rules have been implemented in PRAIS for 2026 reporting. "
"These will appear as errors when users try to save the reporting form. "
"Errors (arising from the application of system validation rules) appear on "
"the forms to highlight any major discrepancies in reported data (see inter-"
"tabular consistency paragraph below). The error message will help the user "
"understand the issue and indicate to the user how to rectify the problem "
"before being allowed to save the form."
msgstr ""
"根据从 2022 年报告流程中吸取的经验教训，PRAIS 为 2026 "
"年报告实施了一系列系统验证规则。当用户尝试保存报告表格时，这些规则将显示为错误。错误（因应用系统验证规则而产生）显示在表格上，以突出报告数据中的任何重大差异（见下文表格间一致性段落）。错误信息将帮助用户了解问题所在，并向用户指出如何纠正问题，然后才允许保存表格。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:428
msgid ""
"Inter-tabular consistency: the total country area and demographics, as "
"presented in the country profile (CP-1.T1 and CP-1.T2), constitute the basis"
" for reporting in many of the other reporting tables. For inter-tabular "
"consistency, the total country, land and water body area as well as total "
"population must not be less than the corresponding area or population "
"estimates in SO1, SO2-3, SO3-1 and SO3-2 tables. The system automatically "
"prefills the total country, land and water body areas and national "
"population in the country profile based on default data. If any reported "
"degraded area, area under drought or populations exposed exceed the values "
"reported in the country profile an error will appear since the percentage "
"value reported cannot normally exceed 100%."
msgstr ""
"表间一致性：国家概况（CP-1.T1 和 "
"CP-1.T2）中列出的国家总面积和人口构成是许多其他报告表的报告基础。为保持表间一致性，国家、陆地和水体总面积以及总人口不得少于 "
"SO1、SO2-3、SO3-1 和 SO3-2 "
"表中相应的面积或人口估计数。系统会根据默认数据自动预填国家概况中的国家、陆地和水体总面积以及国家人口。如果报告的退化面积、干旱面积或暴露人口超过了国家概况中的报告值，则会出现错误，因为报告的百分比值通常不能超过"
" 100%。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:433
msgid ""
"Having negative numbers in tables where only positive numbers are allowed or"
" having non-numeric characters in numeric-only fields also trigger error "
"messages. Regardless of what validation rule triggers the error, the error "
"will prevent the saving of a form and must be rectified by the user before "
"the form can be saved or submitted for review."
msgstr ""
"在只允许输入正数的表格中输入负数或在数字字段中输入非数字字符也会触发错误信息。无论哪种验证规则触发了错误，错误都会阻止保存表单，用户必须在保存表单或提交审核前纠正错误。"

