# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:463
msgid ""
"Information on the total land area, area covered by water bodies, and total "
"country area is required to calculate the proportion of land that is "
"degraded over total land area (SDG indicator 15.3.1), but also to calculate "
"indicators to track progress towards other SOs (e.g. SO 3-1: Trends in the "
"proportion of land under drought over the total land area)."
msgstr ""
"需要有关土地总面积、水体覆盖面积和国家总面积的信息，以计算退化土地占土地总面积的比例（可持续发展目标指标 "
"15.3.1），同时也要计算跟踪其他战略目标进展情况的指标（如战略目标 3-1：干旱土地占土地总面积比例的变化趋势）。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../introduction.md:465
msgid ""
"Total land area, total water bodies area and total country area require "
"respective estimates to be reported in square kilometres (km2) for 2000, "
"2015, 2019 and 2023 or closest available years (to align with the initial "
"and final years of the baseline and reporting periods for SDG indicator "
"15.3.1). Land area data is pre-filled in the reporting table CP-1.T1. "
"Estimates are based on the default land cover data and, as such, they could "
"differ from official national statistics. The pre-filled data can be changed"
" by clicking on the ‘National Data’ switch above the table. However, it is "
"important to ensure consistency with the land cover data and the SDG "
"indicator 15.3.1 estimates. Parties should note that the total country area "
"is auto-calculated in PRAIS from the addition of the total land area and "
"water bodies and is therefore not an editable field."
msgstr ""
"土地总面积、水体总面积和国家总面积要求分别以平方公里（km2）为单位报告 2000、2015、2019 和 2023 "
"年或最接近的可用年份的估计数（以便与可持续发展目标指标 15.3.1 的基线和报告期的初始年份和最后年份保持一致）。土地面积数据已预先填入报告表 "
"CP-1.T1。估算值基于默认的土地覆被数据，因此可能与国家官方统计数据不同。点击表格上方的 \"国家数据 "
"\"开关可更改预填数据。不过，重要的是要确保土地覆被数据与可持续发展目标指标 15.3.1 的估计值保持一致。缔约方应注意，PRAIS "
"中的国家总面积是通过增加土地总面积和水体自动计算得出的，因此不是可编辑字段。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
